    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait r u serious?? that sounds super scary. i thought it was just because i haven't been drinking enough water. if i just drink a ton of water and take a break from the pills for a day or two i'll be fine right? i really dont want to deal with the ER if it's just a minor thing",
