    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear u but its just so expensive and i cant leave work right now. honestly the shakiness isn't even that bad, it's just a little jittery. can i just try taking some extra electrolytes and maybe a magnesium supplement tonight to see if that settles my stomach and helps the tremors? id rather just try that tonight and see how i feel in the morning than rush to the hospital for nothing.",
